<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<body
    style="font-family:'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div
        style="width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-direction: column; background-color: whitesmoke; padding: 1rem 0;">
        <img style="width: 15rem; margin: 1rem;" src="https://clic.epfl.ch/directus/assets/776736f4-ebea-420a-9c5b-3e297e22b782"
            alt="CLIC logo">
        <table
            style="background-color: white; width: 600px; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 5px 5px 20px rgb(191, 191, 191);"
            role="presentation" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <p style="color: gray; font-style: italic;">Hello {{ registration.first_name }},</p>
                    <p>Thank you for ordering the IC faculty's sweater! Here's a summary of what you ordered:</p>
                    <hr style="color: lightgray; border: none; border-top: 1px solid lightgray;">
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <h2>Order Summary:</h2>
                    <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        {% for item in order %}
                        <li style="padding: 0.25rem 0;">{{ item.color }} - {{ item.size }}</li>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <hr style="color: lightgray; border: none; border-top: 1px solid lightgray;">
                    <h2>Payment</h2>
                    <p>You can pay for your order using one of the following methods:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Camipro</strong> at the CLIC office (INM 177) between 12h00 and 13h00 during weekdays until the 27th of March.</li>
                        <li><strong>Bank transfer</strong> via the QR code below (use <a href="{{ qrbill_url }}">this link</a> if it doesn't display)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <center>
                        <img width="550px" src="{{ qrbill_url }}" alt="QR bill for payment"
                            style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 1rem 0;">
                    </center>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <center>
                        <p style="color: gray; font-style: italic; margin-top: 1rem;">Thank you for your order and see you soon!</p>
                    </center>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <center
                        style="background: #FEAE28; background: linear-gradient(45deg,#fe5f03,#ffb940); border-radius: 0.375rem; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.5rem 0;">
                        <p style="padding-top:1rem; color: white;">Follow us on our socials</p>
                        <a href="https://t.me/clicepfl"><img
                                src="https://clic.epfl.ch/directus/assets/e2b444de-87a9-438b-b75e-a6864ba925b2?width=1920"
                                alt="Telegram" style="height:2rem;margin:0 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem"></a>
                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/clicepfl/"><img
                                src="https://clic.epfl.ch/directus/assets/64785955-9d77-42d3-9046-a0f998fabd26?width=1920"
                                alt="Instagram" style="height:2rem;margin:0 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem"></a>
                        <a href="https://twitter.com/CLICepfl"><img
                                src="https://clic.epfl.ch/directus/assets/ef28026f-965c-4f1f-b7a9-eaafea804a07?width=1920"
                                alt="X" style="height:2rem;margin:0 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem"></a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/clicepfl/"><img
                                src="https://clic.epfl.ch/directus/assets/f6cb71fa-e038-4629-b54e-d2fb40fe9666?width=1920"
                                alt="Github" style="height:2rem;margin:0 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem"></a>
                        <a href="mailto:clic@epfl.ch"><img
                                src="https://clic.epfl.ch/directus/assets/b8650fa0-061f-427f-a4a0-97febb99c103?width=1920"
                                alt="Mail CLIC" style="height:2rem;margin:0 0.5rem 1rem 0.5rem"></a>
                    </center>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <img style="width: 10rem; margin: 2rem;" src="https://clic.epfl.ch/directus/assets/f5e0bd00-3f25-4d01-be19-4a7e17c66560"
            alt="CLIC logo footer">
    </div>
</body>

</html>
